title: SPY 2013/14 SNOW PK - TARGA MINI
description:
The Targa Mini packs all the punch of the big boys, but sized just right for small faces. 

The Targa Mini is custom built from a flexible polyurethane frame and features patented Scoop® ventilation system, anti-fog cylindrical dual-lens system with anti-scratch protection, a free bonus lens, ergonomic Isotron™ face foam with moisture-wicking Dri-Force™ fleece, silicone-ribbed strap, 100% UV protection, and is helmet compatible with the most popular helmets on the planet.
